{
  "stem": "16887.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 401.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when he came back, he told me that if I want to get some money, I should go to Ciechanow, where my husband is from, and get the money.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that happened.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were-- that happened just after Kielce pogrom that used to be in Poland.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that time was about 60 people killed by the underground army that were fighting the Russians.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And it was very dangerous for men to travel.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I decided not to let my husband go.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I left my husband with two children.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I said, I'm going to go.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'm going to-- I'm going to-- no, I had no idea that anybody from the family lived.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was going.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I already knew my husband's brother came, which he was only-- he was my brother-in-law.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he was all on-- also my cousin.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I went to get-- actually, I went to go see them and get the money, get some money.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "At that time, like $50 was a fortune.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I embarked to-- to--to-- to go.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was staying in the train like a sardines smashed.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there was a guy, a Polish guy, I remember that he had a little-- a box he was sitting on.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I-- I-- I managed to Polish.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I speak Polish very well.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So he strike up a conversation with me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And in the meantime, he told me to sit down on the box.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And all night long, he was telling me how many Jews he killed.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And if he would have the power, he would kill more of them because look how many survived and look how many came back from Russia.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I didn't say nothing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I always say, you're right.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You're right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You're right, until the morning when the train stopped in Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
